overview:
Imagine if the top-tier culinary professionals in the world got together and shared their favorite places to eat, drink and food shop all over the globe. They have. It’s called Find. Eat. Drink.

MOBILE APP TRAVEL GUIDE Download the Find. Eat. Drink. iPhone app to get restaurant, bar and food shop recommendations from industry insiders - chefs, sommeliers, bartenders, winemakers and food artisans. From hidden haunts to undiscovered watering holes, fine dining to funky dives, these trusted sources pass along local gems

WEBSITE You’ll find Q & As with the pros, plus recipes, cooking tips and trade secrets..
